---
// QuickStart.astro – Quick start section on the landing page
---

<section class="quickstart-section">
  <div class="container quickstart-inner">
    <div class="quickstart-text">
      <h2 class="text-subheading">From zero to orchestration in 30 seconds.</h2>
      <p class="text-body quickstart-body">
        No daemon processes. Just a clean, Git-like CLI that is ready after a
        package-manager install, with optional keyring-backed setup for GitHub and
        AI workflows.
      </p>
      <div class="quickstart-actions">
        <a href="/docs/introduction" class="btn-primary" id="quickstart-cta-docs">
          Read the Docs
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/docs/installation" class="btn-secondary" id="quickstart-cta-install">Installation Guide</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="quickstart-terminal">
      <div class="terminal">
        <div class="terminal-bar">
          <span class="terminal-dot terminal-dot--red"></span>
          <span class="terminal-dot terminal-dot--yellow"></span>
          <span class="terminal-dot terminal-dot--green"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="terminal-body">
          <div class="terminal-line terminal-comment"># Clone all public repos for a GitHub user</div>
          <div class="terminal-line">
            <span class="terminal-prompt">$ </span>
            <span class="terminal-command">git-wrangler clone --user myusername --visibility public</span>
          </div>
          <br />
          <div class="terminal-line terminal-comment"># Commit across all repos at once</div>
          <div class="terminal-line">
            <span class="terminal-prompt">$ </span>
            <span class="terminal-command">git-wrangler commit --message "chore: update deps"</span>
          </div>
          <br />
          <div class="terminal-line terminal-comment"># Rewrite all commit authors</div>
          <div class="terminal-line">
            <span class="terminal-prompt">$ </span>
            <span class="terminal-command">git-wrangler rewrite-authors --name "Jane" --email "jane@dev.io"</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .quickstart-section {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-gray-100);
    padding-block: var(--space-11);
  }

  .quickstart-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-10);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .quickstart-body {
    margin-block: var(--space-6);
  }

  .quickstart-actions {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .quickstart-terminal {
    animation: fade-in 0.5s ease both;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .quickstart-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .quickstart-section {
      padding-block: var(--space-8);
    }
  }
</style>
